    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair, functional condition and would make a reliable project car or daily driver for someone who doesn't mind some character. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dents on the door panels, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few small tears, though all essential electronics and gauges remain operational. It runs and drives, but the engine could benefit from a tune-up, and the suspension is starting to feel a bit soft.",
